OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 1 JUN
OL,4,G1345FMastermind
OL,5,     GClive Myrie hosts the classic
OL,6,     Gquiz where contenders take to the
OL,7,     Gblack chair. Specialist subjects
OL,8,     Ginclude Stephen Hawking, the
OL,9,     Gmusic of Radiohead and Theda Bara.
OL,10,G1415FLightning
OL,11,     GZoe Lyons hosts a quiz where
OL,12,     Gcontestants avoid the light to
OL,13,     Gwin a #3,000 jackpot.
OL,14,G1445FClean It, Fix It
OL,15,     GThe team have one day to help a
OL,16,     Gmother reclaim space in her
OL,17,     Gdaughter's bedroom and playroom
OL,18,     Gand turn the loft space into a
OL,19,     Gusable storage solution.
